response.original_title: The Wedding Present: Valentina -  The Story of a Wedding Present Album
response.overview: A 30 minute documentary (previously only available as part of the book Valentina : The Story of a Wedding Present Album) around the making of Valentina - The Wedding Present's eighth studio album, released in March 2012 by Scopitones.
